r%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3E%3A%20Spencer%20Grant%2FGHI%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrookfield%20Properties%20has%20cut%20several%20executives%20in%20its%20office%20division%20as%20the%20company%20restructures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20has%20evolved%20from%20a%20property-focused%20firm%20into%20a%20Wall%20Street%20fund%20manager%20like%20Blackstone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20structure%20will%20break%20down%20regional%20management%20in%20favor%20of%20national%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBrookfield%20Properties%2C%20which%20operates%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20commercial%20real%20estate%20portfolios%2C%20laid%20off%20a%20handful%20of%20executives%20in%20its%20office%20division%20on%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20downsizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20New%20York%20headquarters%2C%20the%20firm%20let%20go%20of%20three%20office%20leasing%20executives%2C%20an%20executive%20who%20oversees%20asset%20management%2C%20and%20an%20employee%20who%20was%20part%20of%20an%20internal%20group%20that%20manages%20art%20installations%20and%20events%2C%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20cuts%20said.%20Nationally%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20handful%26quot%3B%20of%20people%20were%20let%20go%2C%20including%20roles%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Houston%2C%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrookfield%20Properties%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20property%20investment%20manager%20for%20Brookfield%2C%20an%20investment%20firm%20that%20holds%20more%20than%20%241%20trillion%20in%20assets%2C%20including%2065%20million%20square%20feet%20of%20US%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20internal%20memo%20sent%20to%20Brookfield%20Properties%20employees%20and%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20said%20the%20shift%20reflected%20the%20company's%20transition%20from%20a%20manager%20of%20long-term%20office%20investments%20to%20one%20that%20would%20oversee%20various%20strategies%20and%20that%20would%20need%20to%20reap%20and%20recycle%20capital%20through%20more%20frequent%20asset%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20evolution%20of%20our%20business%20%E2%80%94%20from%20one%20largely%20comprised%20of%20forever-hold%2C%20balance%20sheet%20assets%20to%20a%20mix%20that%20also%20includes%20properties%20held%20in%20fund%20strategies%20with%20varied%20hold%20periods%20and%20return%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20has%20led%20us%20to%20examine%20our%20organizational%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrookfield%20was%20once%20well%20known%20for%20its%20focus%20on%20commercial%20real%20estate%2C%20particularly%20office%20buildings%2C%20such%20as%20Brookfield%20Place%2C%20a%20large%20commercial%20complex%20it%20owns%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan.%20It%20now%20controls%20investments%20across%20categories%20like%20insurance%2C%20credit%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20investment%20firms.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20that%20evolution%20has%20drawn%20comparisons%20to%20other%20major%20asset%20managers%20like%20Blackstone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20move%20restructures%20the%20office%20business's%20management%20and%20operations%2C%20which%20had%20been%20previously%20organized%20around%20regions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20into%20a%20more%20nationally%20focused%20team%2C%20the%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20cuts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Brookfield%20Properties%20appointed%20Bobby%20Swennes%20as%20the%20US%20president%20of%20its%20office%20division.%20Swennes's%20role%20remains%20unchanged%2C%20but%20with%20the%20new%20structure%2C%20Brookfield%20Properties%20announced%20that%20several%20executives%20will%20now%20take%20national%20roles%20under%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20drive%20the%20business%20by%20function%20rather%20than%20geography%2C%20transitioning%20from%20a%20region-head%20model%20to%20a%20function-lead%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20memo%20stated.%20%26quot%3BThis%20structure%20will%20enhance%20portfolio-wide%20strategy%20and%20decision-making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20broader%20shift%20to%20asset%20management%2C%20Brookfield%20Properties%20has%20cut%20back%20on%20in-house%20operations%20personnel%20to%20manage%20its%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20in%20favor%20of%20third-party%20service%20providers.%20Last%20year%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbre.com%2Fpress-releases%2Fcbre-and-brookfield-properties-forge-strategic-partnership%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutsourced%20property%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20US%20office%20portfolio%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20services%20and%20brokerage%20firm%20CBRE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrookfield's%20office%20business%20has%20also%20been%20bruised%20in%20past%20years%20as%20part%20of%20the%20aftereffects%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20reduced%20office%20occupancy%20and%20demand.%20The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-buildings-doom-loop-companies-landlords-remote-work-from-home-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefaulted%20on%20a%20collection%20of%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20towers%20in%20downtown%20Los%20Angeles.%20In%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.costar.com%2Farticle%2F1790928720%2Fbrookfield-properties-lays-off-dozens-of-workers-as-us-construction-slows%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrookfield%20Properties%20laid%20off%20dozens%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20written%20reports%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrookfield's%20focus%20on%20higher-end%20properties%20has%20helped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-office-space-real-estate-fifth-avenue-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20office%20portfolio%20rebound%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20that%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%