the%20actual%20internal%20numbers%2C%20and%20they%20are%20simply%20not%20consistent%20with%20the%20stock's%20performance%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Monteiro%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20sales%20down%20across%20the%20board%20in%20what%20seems%20now%20like%20a%20sustained%20trend%2C%20it's%20very%20hard%20to%20look%20past%20the%20brand%20devaluation%20factor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20could%20also%20move%20to%20make%20life%20harder%20for%20Tesla%20on%20the%20regulatory%20front.%20Tesla%20is%20also%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20a%20flagship%20robotaxi%20service%20in%20Austin%20this%20month%2C%20and%20Musk%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20overhaul%20the%20autonomous%20vehicle%20regulations%20that%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20his%20ambitious%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b31a2ed-90fd-41f6-b511-e3da9c83b65e%5C%22%3ETrump%20threatened%20Musk's%20government%20contracts%2C%20and%20NASA%20relies%20on%20SpaceX%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22white%20crew%20dragon%20spaceship%20with%20nose%20hatch%20open%20in%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d99c3ab8b41a9673faf929%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMusk%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20he'd%20decommission%20the%20SpaceX%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20after%20Trump%20suggested%20he'd%20cut%20Musk's%20government%20contracts.%20Musk%20later%20walked%20back%20the%20idea.%3Cp%3ENASA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20fight%20escalated%2C%20Trump%20said%20on%20TruthSocial%20on%20Thursday%20that%20cutting%20Musk's%20companies'%20government%20contracts%20would%20save%20%26quot%3BBillions%20and%20Billions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonteiro%20said%20that%20if%20Trump%20were%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20his%20threat%2C%20the%20potential%20cut%20to%20government%20contracts%20would%20likely%20impact%20SpaceX%20more%20than%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C