essinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-kanye-west-donald-trump-elon-musk-reconcile-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Ackman%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%20in%20support%20of%20both%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20and%20called%20for%20the%20two%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20peace%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20our%20country.%26quot%3B%20Musk%20didn't%20seem%20completely%20opposed%20to%20extending%20the%20olive%20branch%20with%20Trump%2C%20commenting%20on%20the%20post%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnaval%2Fstatus%2F1930721134368129164%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereshared%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20post%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTech%20needs%20Republicans%20for%20the%20present.%20Republicans%20need%20Tech%20for%20the%20future.%20Drop%20the%20tax%20cuts%2C%20cut%20some%20pork%2C%20get%20the%20bill%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2e27708-695b-46d0-836a-21b5c0836eab%5C%22%3EBoth%20men%20aired%20dirty%20laundry%20about%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20escalating%20feud%20offered%20a%20window%20into%20how%20each%20of%20the%20men%20view%20their%20devolving%20relationship%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20didn't%20appear%20to%20hold%20much%20back%20in%20their%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20posted%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Thursday%20that%20%26quot%3BElon%20was%20'wearing%20thin%2C'%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20asked%20by%20Trump%20to%20leave%20his%20position%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20him%20to%20leave%2C%20I%20took%20away%20his%20EV%20Mandate%20that%20forced%20everyone%20to%20buy%20Electric%20Cars%20that%20nobody%20else%20wanted%20(that%20he%20knew%20for%20months%20I%20was%20going%20to%20do!)%2C%20and%20he%20just%20went%20CRAZY%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Musk%20had%20seen%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Beautiful%20Bill%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20lashed%20out%20against%2C%20and%20only%20developed%20an%20issue%20with%20it%20when%20he%20discovered%20that%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-beautiful-bill-impact-tesla-xai-elon-musk-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20EV%20mandates.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Musk%20fired%20back%2C%20implying%20Trump%20had%20lied%20and%20that%20he%20had%20never%20seen%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20he%20felt%20responsible%20for%20Trump's%20election%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20me%2C%20Trump%20would%20have%20lost%20the%20election%2C%20Dems%20would%20control%20the%20House%20and%20the%20Republicans%20would%20be%2051-49%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20ingratitude%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btime%20to%20drop%20the%20really%20big%20bomb%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Muck%20described%20it%2C%20alleging%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-epstein-files-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20is%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BEpstein%20files%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20reason%20they%20have%20not%20been%20made%20public.%26quot%3B%20(Trump's%20past%20ties%20to%20Epstein%20have%20been%20publicly%20known%2C%20and%20Trump%20has%20said%20the%20two%20had%20a%20falling%20out%20more%20than%2015%20years%20ago%20and%20that%20he%20wasn't%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20convicted%20sex%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20unclear%20if%20Musk%20and%20Trump%20will%20repair%20their%20rift%2C%20Thursday's%20public%20blowup%20made%20one%20thing%20clear%3A%20both%20are%20willing%20to%20roll%20up%20their%20sleeves%20and%20punch%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-elon-musk-fight-takeaways-tesla-spacex-ai-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749239917000%2C%22vi