20hopper%20(left)%20and%20an%20old-school%20grease%20trap%20(right).%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPit%20Boss%20lists%20a%20'rapid%20igniter'%20as%20one%20of%20the%20features%2C%20claiming%20to%20help%20you%20reach%20cooking%20temperatures%20twice%20as%20fast%3B%20I'm%20just%20not%20sure%20what%20it's%20being%20compared%20to.%20From%20a%20cold%20start%2C%20the%20Sportsman%20took%2010%20minutes%20and%2030%20seconds%20to%20reach%20225%20degrees.%20I%20did%20the%20same%20test%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Ftraeger-timberline-grill-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETraeger%20Timberline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20that%20smoker%20only%20took%208%20minutes%20and%2059%20seconds%20to%20reach%20the%20same%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grill%20features%20two%20probe%20ports%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20monitor%20the%20internal%20temperatures%20of%20multiple%20cuts%20simultaneously.%20Only%20one%20probe%20comes%20with%20the%20grill%2C%20however%2C%20so%20a%20second%20one%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-1510980589958-20%26h%3D9dd44e67771522399b12183ac6197ee7fa863cc4f331e645ecd3a18fc049c09d%26postID%3D6843035f7ee75c80592c2a83%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fpit-boss-sportsman-850-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.pitboss-grills.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fpit-boss-meat-probe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchased%20separately%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a073343e-c5cf-4d65-abdf-2080cdfd62fe%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22WiFi%20connectivity%5C%22%3EWiFi%20connectivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20remote%20connection%20to%20a%20smoker%20is%20nearly%20essential%20in%202025.%20I%20know%20people%20who%20would%20prefer%20the%20more%20manual%20process%20of%20smoking%20meat%2C%20but%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20us%2C%20the%20convenience%20of%20checking%20ambient%20and%20probe%20temperature%20away%20from%20the%20house%20is%20magical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sportsman%20850%20supports%20wireless%20connectivity%20via%20WiFi%20or%20Bluetooth%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20close%20you%20are%20to%20the%20grill.%20I%20understand%20the%20necessity%20of%20having%20two%20types%20of%20connection%2C%20but%20I%20found%20that%20it%20led%20to%20a%20slower%20response%20time%3A%20the%20mobile%20app%20needed%20to%20determine%20its%20best%20path%20every%20time%20I%20opened%20it%2C%20leading%20to%20annoying%20delays%20at%20crucial%20cooking%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20screenshots%20of%20the%20PitBoss%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68432ae285e81483682b9de5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEvery%20time%20I%20opened%20the%20app%2C%20I%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20it%20to%20run%20through%20several%20connectivity%20steps%20(left).%20When%20the%20app%20was%20functioning%20well%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20grill%20temperature%20and%20timers%20(right).%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20basic%20level%2C%20the%20app%20is%20fine.%20You%20can%20easily%20see%20and%20change%20the%20temperature%2C%20set%20a%20timer%2C%20and%20see%20connected%20probe%20temps.%20There%20are%20integrated%20recipes%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20save%20them%20as%20your%20favorites.%20There%20are%20even%20how-to%20videos%20buried%20in%20the%20app%20if%20you%20want%20that%20info.%20However%2C%20the%20mobile%20app%20needs%20polish.%20One%20example%20of%20this%20was%20its%20notifications%3A%20When%20I%20turned%20on%20the%20grill%20and%20set%20it%20to%20my%20desired%20temperature%20using%20the%20grill's%20onboard%20controller%2C%20it%20didn't%20send%20an%20app%20notification%20when%20it%20reached%20its%20goal.%20A%20small%20detail%2C%20but%20in%20comparison%2C%20Traeger's%20app%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20reliable%20with%20the%20same%20task.%20(Read%20more%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-traeger-grill%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20Traeger%20grills%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20the%20app%20graphs%20ambient%20and%20probe%20temperatures%2C%20but%20this%20feature%20never%20worked%20for%20me%20over%20several%20weeks%20and%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20uses.%20The%20app's%20cooking%20history%20log%20was%20also%20unreliable%2C%20sometimes%20listing%20multiple%20cooks%20with%200%3A00%20times%20or%20listing%20the%20wrong%20duration%20of%20time%20when%20it%20did%20recognize%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a67fe46-a4fd-4881-a508-ee994d603f15%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smoking%20performance%5C%22%3ESmoking%20performance%20is%20great%20but%20not%20perfect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22steaks%20on%20the%20pitboss%20grill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684328ca85e81483682b9d74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tested%20the%20Sportsman%20850%20with%20many%20different%20types%20of%20foods%2C%20including%20steak.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sportsman%20850%20performed%20well%20and%20proved%20reliable%20for%20smoking%20meat%20and%20other%20kinds%20of%20food.%20Though%20I'm%20not%20convinced%20the%20rapid%20igniter%20makes%20much%20of%20a%20difference%2C%20the%20Sportsman%20did%20reach%20target%20temperatures%20quickly%20and%20in%20line%20with%20recipe%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20aspect%20of%20the%20smoker%20is%20its%20temperature%20retention.%20My%20periodic%20temperature%20checks%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%20indicate%20that%20the%20grill%20keeps%20a%20consistent%20temperature%2C%20only%20fluctuating%20briefly%20a%20few%20times%2C%20usually%20on%20the%20hotter%20side%20by%205%20to%2010%20degrees.%20This%20is%20normal%20behavior%20for%20a%20smoker.%20Similarly%2C%20using%20the%20mobile%20app%20to%20check%20its%20reported%20temperature%20indicated%20the%20same%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20smoked%20several%20racks%20of%20ribs%2C%20a%20small%20turkey%20breast%2C%20steaks%2C%20and%20experimented%20with%20boneless%20country-style%20ribs%20and%20fresh%20ears%20of%20corn.%20Cooking%20the%20meat%20I%20was%20familiar%20with%20came%20out%20as%20expected%20and%20nearly%20identical%20to%20other%20smokers.%20I%20was%20equally%20as%20satisfied%20with%20the%20new%20recipes%20I%20looked%20up%20online%20and%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pit%20Boss%20mobile%20app%20has%20a%20decent%20number%20of%20recipes%20to%20get%20you%20started%20if%20you%20need%20them.%20I%20liked%20how%20the%20recipe%20directions%20have%20a%20checkbox%20next%20to%20each%20step%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20keep%20track%20of%20where%20you%20are%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20hopper's%2021-pound%20capacity%20sufficient%2C%20but%20its%20tall%20and%20narrow%20design%2C%20along%20with%20a%20non-removable%20security%20grate%20at%20the%20top%2C%20made%20it%20hard%20to%20push%20the%20pellets%20down%20if%20they%20didn't%20always%20filter%20in%20smoothly%20during%20a%20smoking%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20close%20up%20of%20the%20sportsman's%20flame%20broiler%20lever%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68432cf885e81483682b9e64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20signature%20feature%20of%20the%20Sportsman%20850%20is%20the%20Flame%20Broiler%20lever%20(shown%20left%20and%20under%20the%20grill%20grate)%2C%20which%20exposes%20the%20broiler%20for%20more%20direct%20heat.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Flame%20Broiler%20lever%20is%20a%20neat%20addition%2C%20I'm%20unsure%20about%20its%20general%20need.%20I%20used%20it%20on%20steaks%20to%20give%20them%20a%20sear%20and%20it%20worked%20well.%20But%20after%20spending%20time%20with%20the%20lever%2C%20my%20concern%20isn't%20around%20its%20functionality%2C%20but%20how%20much%20it's%20needed.%20Beyond%20searing%20steak%2C%20I%20didn't%20find%20many%20situations%20where%20I'd%20want%20to%20engage%20it%20for%20extra%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20aware%2C%20too%2C%20that%20when%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20grease%20or%20food%20remnants%20they%20can%20catch%20fire%20when%20the%20Flame%20Broiler%20is%20engaged.%20I%20noticed%20the%20dirty%20grates%20causing%20sparking%20and%20embers%20when%20exposed%20to%20the%20fire%2C%20which%20was%20only%20several%20inches%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbaa2acc-6e28-4f4d-8af9-1c78d27fd045%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20pit%20boss%20control%20panel%20and%20rusting%20on%20the%20ignitor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6843287d85e81483682b9d6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20of%20the%20big%20cons%20of%20the%20smoker%20are%20its%20control%20panel%20(left)%2C%20which%20is%20confusing%20and%20hard%20to%20see%2C%20and%20its%20durability%20(right)%20%E2%80%94%20I%20noticed%20rusting%20after%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20use.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20tested%20the%20850%2C%20the%20digital%20controller%20stood%20out%20as%20a%20weak%20spot.%20Its%20biggest%20problem%20is%20that%20it's%20positioned%20low%2C%20so%20you%20need%20to%20bend%20down%20to%20see%20i