E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20say%20whether%20T-Mobile's%20coverage%20works%20for%20you%20and%20your%20area%2C%20and%20while%20T-Mobile's%20coverage%20map%20can%20give%20you%20an%20idea%2C%20no%20carrier%20coverage%20map%20is%20truly%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20take%20from%20T-Mobile's%20website%20showing%20coverage%20for%20Alaska%20as%20of%20May%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f82b2c6ad288d1481b498%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ET-Mobile's%20Alaska%20coverage%20covers%20the%20same%20areas%20that%20other%20major%20carriers%20cover.%3Cp%3ET-Mobile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20determine%20if%20T-Mobile%20works%20well%20in%20your%20area%20is%20to%20ask%20local%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20neighbors.%20You%20can%20also%20check%20local%20groups%20on%20social%20media%20channels%2C%20like%20Facebook%20and%20Nextdoor.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20take%20from%20T-Mobile's%20website%20showing%20coverage%20for%20the%20Hawaii%20as%20of%20May%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f82cfc6ad288d1481b49f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ET-Mobile's%20coverage%20in%20Hawaii%20is%20excellent.%3Cp%3ET-Mobile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20says%20T-Mobile's%20coverage%20isn't%20good%2C%20ask%20which%20carrier%20works%20for%20them.%20You%20might%20find%20that%20no%20carrier%20works%20well%20in%20that%20area%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20around%20my%20home.%20I%20fully%20realize%20the%20irony%20that%20someone%20writing%20a%20carrier%20review%20has%20poor%20coverage%20from%20every%20major%20carrier.%20Don't%20worry%2C%20I%20venture%20out%20to%20various%20spots%20in%20and%20out%20of%20town%20to%20test%20signal%20strength%20and%20data%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246419537-5497-4736-b9d5-38d918a2fdf1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Data%20speeds%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20speeds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ET-Mobile%20advertises%20data%20speeds%20between%2079%20and%20357%20Mbps%20on%20its%20Essentials%20plans%2C%20and%20between%2089%20and%20418%20Mbps%20on%20its%20Beyond%20plans.%20Our%20speed%20tests%20varied%20wildly%2C%20regardless%20of%20plans%20%E2%80%94%20as%20high%20as%20902%20Mbps%20in%20busy%20parts%20of%20town%2C%20to%20as%20low%20as%200.97%20Mbps%20in%20leafy%20residential%20areas%20not%20too%20far%20away%20from%20the%20busy%20section.%20Interestingly%2C%20I%20saw%20fast%20speeds%20up%20to%20303%20Mbps%20in%20sparsely%20populated%20%26quot%3Bback-country%26quot%3B%20parts%20of%20my%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20from%20a%20computer%20showing%20two%20data%20speed%20tests%20on%20T-Mobile's%20network%2C%20the%20top%20being%20the%20fastests%20and%20the%20bottom%20being%20the%20slowest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6835c2d96ffb6822ec617fb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fastest%20and%20slowest%20speeds%20we%20saw%20on%20T-Mobile's%20network%20were%20drastically%20different%2C%20but%20this%20is%20typical%20for%20all%20carriers.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3B%20Speedtest.net%20app%20used%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20T-Mobile%20data%20speeds%20will%20differ%20nationwide%2C%20and%20even%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20my%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20speed%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20plans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20data%20speeds%20in%20my%20test%20areas%2C%20the%20difference%20in%20data%20speeds%20between%20the%20Essentials%20plan%20and%20the%20Experience%20Beyond%20plan%20can%20be%20translated%20to%20almost%20anyone%20across%20the%20coun