e%20CEO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664cf2e314fb5b23cc5eda4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223892%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYouTube%20CEO%20Neal%20Mohan.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Mazur%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYouTube%20is%20adding%20a%20new%20tool%20to%20let%20creators%20change%20thumbnails%20for%20videos%20in%20different%20languages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20part%20of%20a%20push%20by%20YouTube%20to%20help%20videos%20travel%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI-powered%20dubbing%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20among%20YouTube%20stars%20like%20MrBeast.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-is-trying-to-ahead-of-netflix-advertising-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20releasing%20a%20new%20feature%20to%20help%20creators%20spread%20their%20content%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%2C%20which%20will%20be%20rolling%20out%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20lets%20creators%20upload%20different%20thumbnails%20for%20each%20video%20that's%20dubbed%20into%20a%20different%20language%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20influencers%20localize%20their%20thumbnails%20based%20on%20a%20viewer's%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20is%20available%20to%20a%20subset%20of%20creators%20who%20have%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-youtube-feature-lets-creators-add-multiple-language-audio-tracks-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube's%20dubbing%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20always%20testing%20more%20ways%20for%20creators%20to%20reach%20new%20audiences.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20creators%20are%20able%20to%20localize%20their%20thumbnails%20for%20videos%20with%20multiple%20language%20audio%20tracks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20YouTube%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20YouTube's%20top%20stars%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-tells-mark-zuckerberg-what-he-would-change-about-facebook-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20bullish%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20dub%20videos%20so%20they%20can%20reach%20global%20audiences.%20YouTube%20began%20testing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-youtube-feature-lets-creators-add-multiple-language-audio-tracks-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emulti-language%20audio%20dubbing%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20some%20creators%20as%20early%20as%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20thumbnail%20feature%20opens%20up%20an%20additional%20opportunity%20for%20creators%20to%20make%20their%20videos%20feel%20more%20native%20to%20a%20viewer's%20location%2C%20said%20Nate%20Stone%2C%20cofounder%20at%20the%20AI%20dubbing%20platform%20DittoDub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDittoDub%20is%20offering%20a%20tool%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20detect%20the%20text%20in%20a%20creator's%20thumbnail%20in%20order%20to%20change%20its%20language%20for%20each%20dubbed%20video.%20Creators%20with%20access%20to%20YouTube's%20new%20multi-language%20thumbnail%20feature%20can%20then%20upload%20those%20custom%20thumbnails%20to%20their%20YouTube%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDittoDub%20said%20its%20translation%20tools%20are%20reviewed%20by%20humans%20to%20ensure%20a%20high%20level%20of%20confidence%20that%20it's%20preserving%20the%20meaning%20in%20any%20translated%20audio%20or%20visuals.%20They%20want%20to%20capture%20the%20creator's%20original%20tone%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emotion%20that%20we%20always%20strive%20for%20is%20not%20to%20recreate%20something%20different%2C%20but%20instead%20to%20preserve%20all%20of%20the%20original%20intentions%20of%20the%20creator%2C%26quot%3B%20Stone%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines