ng%20the%20microgreens%2C%20he%20became%20a%20vocal%20advocate%20for%20the%20health%20benefits%20of%20these%20tiny%20plants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oncologist%20told%20me%20that%20microgreens%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20not%20only%20for%20his%20patients%20but%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322864%2Fkochi-aathira-sethumadhavan-pcos-weight-loss-healthy-diet-nutrition-sustainable-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanyone%20seeking%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20says.%20This%20feedback%20gave%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20push%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jatin%20Sarin%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20in%20oncology%20based%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCancer%20is%20increasingly%20recognised%20as%20a%20lifestyle%20disease%2C%20with%20poor%20dietary%20habits%20playing%20a%20major%20role.%20Our%20food%20today%20is%20often%20packed%20with%20chemicals%20and%20has%20fewer%20essential%20nutrients.%20Microgreens%2C%20however%2C%20are%20a%20different%20story.%20These%20young%20plants%2C%20which%20are%20harvested%20after%20the%20sprout%20stage%2C%20are%20packed%20with%20micronutrients%20and%20offer%20a%20wealth%20of%20health%20benefits.%20They%20can%20be%20a%20valuable%20addition%20to%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20diet%2C%20complementing%20conventional%20treatments%20like%20chemotherapy%20and%20radiotherapy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMicrogreens%20are%20rich%20in%20vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20making%20them%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20anyone%20looking%20to%20boost%20their%20overall%20health%20and%20well-being.%20I%20have%20included%20them%20in%20my%20diet%20and%20have%20noticed%20an%20improvement%20in%20my%20energy%20levels%20and%20overall%20vitality.%20Their%20nutritional%20density%20makes%20them%20an%20ideal%20food%20for%20maintaining%20health%2C%20preventing%20illness%2C%20and%20promoting%20a%20healthier%20lifestyle%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20oncologist%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kuldeep%20Singh%2C%20learning%20about%20microgreens%20farming%20proved%20to%20be%20beneficial%20for%20gaining%20profits.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20met%20Mohit%20at%20the%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20he%20was%20giving%20a%20talk%20on%20modern%20farming%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20farmer%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrepreneur%20started%20with%20just%2021%20varieties%20of%20seeds%2C%20but%20now%20he%20grows%20over%2075%20varieties%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220103.646_11zon-1749054673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444412%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20started%20with%20just%2021%20varieties%20of%20seeds%2C%20but%20now%20he%20grows%20over%2075%20varieties%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20did%20not%20think%20of%20attending%20it%2C%20but%20what%20he%20said%20about%20using%20less%20space%20and%20water%20caught%20my%20attention.%20We%20were%20always%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20improve%20our%20yields%20with%20the%20limited%20land%20we%20had%2C%20and%20his%20techniques%20seemed%20like%20the%20solution%20we%20were%20searching%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20he%20has%20shifted%20to%20microgreens%20farming%2C%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20hard%20work%20and%20learning%20have%20seen%20a%20positive%20result.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20could%20grow%206%2C500%20cauliflower%20bulbs%20in%205%20kanal%20of%20land.%20After%20learning%20from%20Mohit%2C%20we%20now%20produce%20over%2020%2C000%20bulbs%20in%20the%20same%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20proudly.%20The%20method%20also%20helped%20the%20farmer%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297512%2Findian-farmers-agroforestry-climate-change-solution-agriculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincrease%20his%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CMicrogreens%20farming%20allowed%20us%20to%20diversify%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20producing%20different%20seeds%20like%20cabbage%20and%20radish%20for%20Greenu%2C%20which%20has%20opened%20up%20a%20new%20stream%20of%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20training%20initiative%2C%20the%2046-year-old%20has%20taught%20over%20300%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20minimal%20space%20to%20grow%20these%20high-value%20crops%2C%20helping%20them%20earn%20more%20with%20fewer%20resources.%20He%20also%20came%20across%20the%20incubation%20centre%20in%20Hisar%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20RKVY%20Raftaar%20scheme.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20business%20received%20support%20and%20funding%20through%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETiny%20greens%2C%20big%20impact%3A%20How%20Greenu%20expanded%20to%20growing%20over%2075%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Greenu%20entrepreneur%20believes%20that%20the%20beauty%20of%20microgreens%20farming%20lies%20in%20its%20simplicity%20and%20efficiency.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20venture%20by%20selecting%20high-quality%20and%20non%20genetically%20modified%20(non-GMO)%20seeds.%20I%20source%20mine%20from%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendras%20(KVK)%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20organic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20seeds%20are%20sown%20in%20sterilised%20growing%20media%2C%20like%20cocopeat%20or%20coco%20coir%2C%20in%20trays.%20The%20microgreens%20are%20watered%20with%20a%20minimal%20amount%20of%20just%2030%20ml%20of%20water%20per%20tray%20daily.%20He%20does%20not%20use%20any%20chemicals%20or%20pesticides%20in%20his%20farming%20and%20only%20believes%20in%20following%20organic%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20a%20considerable%20investment%20of%20around%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20a%20small-scale%20microgreens%20operations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-04T220435.276_11zon-1749054886-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-444415%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20considerable%20investment%20of%20around%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20you%20can%20set%20up%20a%20small-scale%20microgreens%20operation%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20seven%20to%2010%20days%2C%20these%20greens%20are%20ready%20to%20be%20harvested.%20But%20the%20entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is%20unique%20as%20he%20often%20sends%20the%20microgreens%20out%20to%20customers%20in%20their%20live%20state%2C%20with%20roots%20intact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20sure%20they%20retain%20their%20nutrients%20for%20longer.%20Restaurants%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20the%20end%20customers%20realise%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20because%20they%20get%20the%20fresh%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20started%20with%20just%2021%20varieties%20of%20seeds%2C%20but%20now%20he%20grows%20over%2075%2C%20including%20broccoli%2C%20radish%2C%20mustard%2C%20and%20even%20millet%20microgreens%2C%20which%20are%20rich%20in%20calcium%20and%20vitamin%20B12%2C%20in%20a%20500-square-foot%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E