sweetness%2C%20into%20science%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20circular%20solutions.%20What%20if%20this%20humble%20crop%20could%20also%20help%20solve%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20environmental%20problems%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20producer%20of%20sugarcane%2C%20cultivating%20over%20400%20million%20tonnes%20annually%20across%20nearly%205%20million%20hectares%20of%20farmland%20(Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20%26amp%3B%20Farmers%20Welfare%2C%202023).%20For%20millions%20of%20farmers%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20sugarcane%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20cash%20crop.%20It%20is%20a%20vital%20source%20of%20income%2C%20tied%20closely%20to%20the%20rural%20economy%2C%20employment%2C%20and%20agrarian%20livelihoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sugarcane%E2%80%99s%20potential%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20at%20jaggery%2C%20sugar%2C%20or%20juice.%20Each%20harvest%20also%20produces%20vast%20quantities%20of%20agricultural%20residue%20%E2%80%94%20bagasse%2C%20molasses%2C%20and%20press%20mud%20%E2%80%94%20that%20often%20go%20underutilised.%20In%20a%20country%20simultaneously%20battling%20mounting%20plastic%20pollution%20and%20looking%20for%20climate-resilient%20circular%20economy%20solutions%2C%20these%20byproducts%20offer%20an%20untapped%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20is%20grappling%20with%20a%20serious%20waste%20management%20challenge.%20The%20country%20generates%20over%205%20million%20tonnes%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20waste%20each%20year%2C%20much%20of%20which%20remains%20non-recyclable%20and%20persistent%20in%20the%20environment%20(Source%3A%20UNEP%2C%20CPCB).%20As%20global%20and%20domestic%20regulations%20tighten%20around%20plastic%20use%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20viable%2C%20biodegradable%20alternatives%20is%20not%20only%20growing%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20essential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20clas